NDI® Software Development Kit License Agreement
================================================

This license token (NDI-SDK) gates installation of media-libs/libndi,
the proprietary NewTek/Vizrt NDI SDK runtime. The full license text
ships inside the SDK tarball downloaded from ndi.video.

After accepting the agreement, add to /etc/portage/make.conf:

    ACCEPT_LICENSE="${ACCEPT_LICENSE} NDI-SDK"

or as a per-package override in /etc/portage/package.license:

    media-libs/libndi NDI-SDK

The verbatim agreement is installed by the libndi ebuild to:

    /usr/share/doc/libndi-<version>/licenses/NDI-SDK-License.txt

